BUT REMEMBER :- the way of extending thread class is not ok. because the same will not allow us to extend more classes if required.
so the thread class implements the runnable interface which all the run method (See by control click)

so we can directly implements it so that we can extend classes but still there is a problem , how can we run the code or call run() method

so we create 2 threads passing the reference variable of Runnable (obj1 , obj2) in constructor